description:
&lt;p&gt;As a specialist musculoskeletal Podiatrist, you will be working in a multi-disciplinary clinic with direct contact with GPwSI, Orthopaedics, rheumatologists, physiotherapists, Advanced practice physiotherapists.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be able to provide neurological &amp; biomechanical assessment of foot, ankle and lower leg to identify the correct management plan or patient pathway using best practice and evidenced based medicine.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful applicant will be competent or willing to work towards competencies in:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Insole manufacture&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Custom made orthotic manufacture/casting and prescribing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;IRMER (onsite radiology department )&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Biomechanical examinations /Complex musculoskeletal examinations and treatment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use of Optogait&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient in rehabilitation or exercise management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We monitor the outcomes of podiatric medicine treatments and undertake audits to understand the effects, constantly seeking to empower clinicians to evolve and improve the service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Person Specification:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum of 2 years post qualification experience as a HcpC registered Podiatrist (2 years of these in MSK speciality)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Registered with the Health and Care Professions Council (HCPC)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A qualification at degree level for Podiatric medicine&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evidence of accredited post-graduate training and CPD relevant to; the management of musculoskeletal conditions and pain within the biopsychosocial model of care.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate an understanding and involvement of Clinical Governance and risk assessment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Additional benefits of joining Circle Health:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;27 days’ annual leave with additional days for long-term service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cycle to work scheme: save money on a new bike and benefit from interest-free instalments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Private pension scheme helping your to live well in retirement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Health and wellbeing programme which includes free fruit, massages and fitness sessions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Employee assistance programme: get confidential support 24/7&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Private medical insurance to help you get any treatment you need quickly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Non-contributory life assurance and income protection insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perkbox for employee discounts at a range of retailers, restaurants and other services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free Uniform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Season ticket loan: get the benefit of an annual ticket and pay the cost over 12 months&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
